data.description: If you're looking for rolling hills, wide open spaces, room to roam, & a home built for beauty, atmosphere, comfort, convenience, & entertaining, then look no further. Come home to this spacious & well planned home in beautiful Pueblo West. The house sits atop 1.35 rolling acres, w/ gorgeous views in every direction. Immediately upon entering, you are struck with a sense of spaciousness due to the vaulted ceilings & open floor plan. The main level features a formal dining room, spacious living room, kitchen, breakfast nook, two large bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, & laundry room. The Living Room ambience is complete with a gas log fireplace, wood burning stove, & walk-out door to a deck with views of the mountains & Pueblo Reservoir. The kitchen is open, conveniently laid out w/ tile counter tops, reverse osmosis water filtration system, pantry, counter bar, all kitchen appliances, & breakfast nook. The Master Bedroom features an adjoining master bath w/ large soaking tub, free-standing shower, & walk-in closet. The enormous finished basement area boasts new carpet, family room for entertaining, perfect area for home theater, 2 additional bedrooms, full bath, & giant storage area. There is a 3 car, oversized garage w/automatic opener. To complete this perfection is a 30x40 insulated SHOP/BARN that is complete w/ wood stove, electricity, LED lights, & concrete floors. The SHOP/BARN can be used as a boat house, barn for horses, or additional toy/car parking!!!
